{"tid":1069084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時覺得香港d野賣得貴 唔係無原因","createTime":"2019-03-19T16:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T17:04:39.000Z","uid":121265,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c5a02696f2314b9914f583a17f76990b2003759","tid":1069084,"uid":121265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T16:55:08.000Z","msg":"姐係咁 我雖然唔係成日淘寶 <br />\n但見到香港既所謂小店 網店<br />\n真係唔抵幫 大陸野都賣咁貴 又無租 又無員工 <br />\n香港地貴係租金 人工 唔係product <br />\n良心呢？<br />\n<br />\n買果d都唔抵幫啦 自己又買貴左<br />\n幫助香港成為物價高城市<br />\n仲助長佢地愈賣愈貴 愈黎愈誇張<br />\n我就覺得一件t-shirt <br />\n無design 無fashion 無brand 既野都賣到$150咁<br />\n就真係有道理 有market 有demand 有supply <br />\n<br />\n所以我地香港終於拎全球第一 唔係無原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/307629/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C6%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%B2%BB%E6%9C%80%E8%B2%B4%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC%E5%B9%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E8%25AA%25AA%2F307629%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25BA%258C6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E6%259C%2580%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258E%2592%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E5%25B9%25BE&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9NB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=94e69aa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA/307629/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C6%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E8%B2%BB%E6%9C%80%E8%B2%B4%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC%E5%B9%BE</a><br />\n<br />\n另附上良心網店及淘寶link<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsNVxMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsNVxMu.png&h=13dd8f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nm6SzZR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.